ER24 Metro Fire and other services attended to the incident on Prince George Drive in Muizenberg and found the man lying on the road.The vehicle that collided with the man was not found at the scene. He was estimated to have been flung at least 50 to 60 metres when he was hit by the vehicle. Upon assessment it was found that he sustained multiple severe injuries. Sadly there was nothing that could be done for the man and he was declared dead said ER24 spokesperson Chitra Bodasing Harduth.